# CODEOWNERS — the human PR review gate for the agentic harness.
#
# 🟩 NATIVE enforcement: when the repository ruleset requires CODEOWNERS review
# (set by harness/deploy/github/enforce-protections.ps1), GitHub itself BLOCKS merge
# until an owner listed here approves the PR. This is the harness's "Human (PR gate)"
# row — real platform enforcement, not orchestration. Replace @your-org/your-team with the
# real reviewing owner/team when you instantiate the harness into your own repo.

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
*                    @your-org/your-team

# Application source — the system under test.
/src/                @your-org/your-team

# The governance harness itself (agents, prompts, workflows, issue forms).
/.github/            @your-org/your-team

# CI scripts + the orchestrator/dispatcher (the layered 🟦 logic).
/ci/                 @your-org/your-team
/orchestrator/       @your-org/your-team
